Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:10.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.80,0:00:10.10,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.41,0:00:14.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪會選擇相信哪一個呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:20.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs60\fad(1500,0)}家族套餐
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.50,0:00:25.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我而言 櫻見塔是回憶之地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.56,0:00:29.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(497,518)}14年前\h\h\h\h\h\h\h櫻見塔
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.51,0:00:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,14年前的那一天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.75,0:00:34.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被拋棄於此
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.26,0:00:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次去那邊 快點快點
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.79,0:00:43.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就回來 在這裡等著哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.51,0:00:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就回來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.71,0:00:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我很快就回來 我很快就回來…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.18,0:01:01.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是糟透了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.97,0:01:03.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.75,0:01:06.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果今天是最糟糕的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.46,0:01:09.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就意味著明天只會比今天更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:11.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.72,0:01:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…是誰?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.54,0:01:16.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.12,0:01:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父母呢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.96,0:01:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.11,0:01:22.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.43,0:01:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那跟我來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.59,0:01:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是我們的邂逅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.89,0:01:33.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他的名字叫作戰場馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.54,0:01:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他和我一樣都是被拋棄的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.71,0:01:56.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 為什麼要跟著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.84,0:01:58.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「為什麼」是指?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.46,0:02:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是比我低一年級嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.45,0:02:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然是這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.92,0:02:03.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別老跟著我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.88,0:02:07.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,趕緊變得獨立一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.72,0:02:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:43.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在寫什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.49,0:02:46.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於馬克 又打架了的事
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.58,0:02:49.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 別整天只顧著我
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.06,0:02:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也去關心點別的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.76,0:02:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世間的事啊 自己的事啊什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.38,0:02:58.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就好 如果沒有馬克就不會有現在的我了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.61,0:03:09.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.20,0:03:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好希望能在這裡進行婚禮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.40,0:03:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊?在這麼偏僻的地方嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.41,0:03:18.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和馬克說的一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.46,0:03:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克把我的最糟變成了最好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.41,0:03:25.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望能在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.16,0:03:32.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35}馬克和高年級的學生吵架了\N能不能稍微變得老實點呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:37.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙到底算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.57,0:03:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超不爽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.06,0:03:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得在表現自己一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.42,0:03:42.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像自己很不幸一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.98,0:03:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊 而且還有男人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.43,0:03:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那個吧 那個飛機頭
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.89,0:03:51.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶吶 要不要收拾一下那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.77,0:03:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35}有重要的事要對你說。\N一個人到鎮外廢棄工廠來\N馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.10,0:04:04.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克 你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.33,0:04:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吶 馬克 快回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.02,0:04:16.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 真的來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.39,0:04:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 好可愛 不好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.53,0:04:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,萬一她說出去了怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.15,0:04:26.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事沒事 聽說她沒有父母的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.72,0:04:28.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能和誰去說啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.67,0:04:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且我們還未成年
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.77,0:04:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.39,0:04:36.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35}我到廢棄工廠了 你在哪裡？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:36.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.04,0:04:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.43,0:04:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放開我!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.84,0:04:42.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.07,0:04:48.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不接
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.93,0:04:53.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 為什麼不接啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.51,0:04:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,廢棄工廠是什麼意思啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.01,0:05:02.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這股不詳感是怎麼回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.76,0:05:25.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.01,0:05:31.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我能陪在你身邊的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.90,0:05:35.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就不會遇到這樣的事了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.70,0:05:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會變成這樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.96,0:05:51.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 已經完了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.88,0:05:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事到如今…已經無法挽回了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:00.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.73,0:06:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.56,0:06:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果馬克感到痛苦的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.74,0:06:08.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就由我來保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:10.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難過的話
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.94,0:06:12.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就陪你一起哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.59,0:06:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.58,0:06:20.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要留下我一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.60,0:06:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會留下你一人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.15,0:06:30.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會保護你的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.87,0:06:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由我來保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:36.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直到世界終結 愛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.17,0:06:50.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:03.63,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}The girl with the sharp thorn in her flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:03.63,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}渾身長滿棘刺的女子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:06.25,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I meet you at your story
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.63,0:07:06.25,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我與你相逢在你的故事中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:11.34,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Behind the hatred there lies a murderous love
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.26,0:07:11.34,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}憎惡背後滿載致命的愛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:14.02,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Do you kill your friends
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.45,0:07:14.02,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你是否會殺死朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:16.63,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}If you can fulfill your wish?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.02,0:07:16.63,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如果能滿足一己之願?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:19.25,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Can you die for someone?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.63,0:07:19.25,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你是否願為他人而死?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:22.35,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}They are synonymous words
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.25,0:07:22.35,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}二者皆同義詞
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:24.92,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Life is a game  It's a survival  That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.35,0:07:24.92,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}生存是場遊戲  即為倖存者  沒錯!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.51,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}How do you start?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.92,0:07:27.51,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你將如何開始?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:30.24,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Time and Space  It's a crossroad  through a gate!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.51,0:07:30.24,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}時空是穿過大門的十字路口!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:33.14,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Where do you go?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.24,0:07:33.14,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你將去往何處?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:35.62,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}You seek eternal breath
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.14,0:07:35.62,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你尋求著永恆之氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:37.54,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Why do you need to live?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.69,0:07:37.54,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}你為何而活?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:42.91,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We don't know when this world came into being
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.54,0:07:42.91,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我們不知這個世界何時誕生
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.78,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}We are the timeleaper
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.91,0:07:44.78,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我們是時空跳躍者
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:47.79,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Nothing's gonna change with you in the world
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.78,0:07:47.79,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}在這個世界裡 你一如往昔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:50.82,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Everything will be decided by the rules
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.79,0:07:50.82,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一切將遵循著既定規則
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:55.63,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Oh,We are traveling the past and the future through love
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.82,0:07:55.63,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}是啊,我們在愛的交織中穿梭於過去及未來
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.63,0:07:56.29,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Break out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.63,0:07:56.29,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}爆發!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:08:01.34,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Let's dial back all the pains and we will be born again
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.29,0:08:01.34,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}讓我們回撥一切傷痛繼而重生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:03.96,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}I wanna see the stars with you
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.34,0:08:03.96,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}我想和你一起看群星
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:07.02,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}Over the miracle
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.96,0:08:07.02,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}穿越奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:13.83,OP_eng,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}It's not a Dead END
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.02,0:08:13.83,OP_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}這並非終結



Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.46,0:08:23.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:24.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.27,0:08:31.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀 您就過來這邊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.06,0:08:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸他…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.94,0:08:41.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然欺騙了我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.62,0:08:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪 他們打算到上面去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.63,0:08:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.76,0:08:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.80,0:08:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定他們有逃離的辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.08,0:08:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.90,0:08:55.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35}7/7  12:45  [櫻見塔第一展望台]\N由乃奪回被7th搶走的手機\N7/7  12:48  [櫻見塔第一展望台]\N發生了爆炸\N7/7  13:02  [櫻見塔第一展望台]\N7th他們背著爸爸前往第二展望台
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.25,0:08:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,利用降落傘逃離？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.30,0:08:57.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.49,0:09:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們去打倒他們 把降落傘搶過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.68,0:09:01.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.71,0:09:04.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前不是輸了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且現在還有傷在身
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.77,0:09:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我們輸的理由非常明顯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.02,0:09:11.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個要怪阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:13.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狀況其實是「二對一」 所以我們輸了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.56,0:09:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.06,0:09:19.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我沒能成為戰力
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.86,0:09:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 正好相反
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.84,0:09:23.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.75,0:09:27.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們只要用我們的做法就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.94,0:09:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(634,526)}同時\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h[兒童養護設施  母親之家]
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.76,0:09:40.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？櫻見塔…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.22,0:09:42.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了不明原因的爆炸並起火
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.94,0:09:44.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有崩塌的危險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.54,0:09:50.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且 天野雪輝的病房裡發現了「我去櫻見塔」的留言
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.36,0:09:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事態有可能發展成危急狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.64,0:09:56.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,立刻聯絡雪輝君的母親
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.41,0:09:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.24,0:10:01.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn微軟雅黑\fs40\pos(767,665)}server
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.76,0:10:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒找到8th的服務器
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.67,0:10:07.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…這是調虎離山？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.07,0:10:19.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克 他們追來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.62,0:10:20.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:23.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我讓你別管1st
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.54,0:10:26.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,盡早把未來日記破壞不就好了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.65,0:10:27.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.05,0:10:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到那種窩囊廢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.60,0:10:31.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不經意就多管閒事了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.73,0:10:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過能在這座塔裡舉行儀式真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.13,0:10:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.72,0:10:40.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.49,0:10:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我們的夢想
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.06,0:10:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們會永遠在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.10,0:10:53.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和他們做個了結吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.40,0:10:54.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們能贏嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:10:59.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的愛是不會輸給他們那種虛偽的愛的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:01.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.25,0:11:04.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 就算是1st這次也會反省
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.96,0:11:07.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後拚死攻過來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.56,0:11:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看 他們來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.12,0:11:13.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 走吧 愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好 馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.18,0:11:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2nd？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.35,0:11:26.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1st去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.25,0:11:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我太弱 所以躲起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.41,0:11:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1st？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.90,0:11:34.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前我會輸的理由只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.47,0:11:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是因為我置身於危險之中
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.13,0:11:39.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.22,0:11:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本沒有反省？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.32,0:11:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 7th 我們要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.57,0:11:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 7th 我們要上了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.63,0:11:56.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「要上了」算什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.03,0:11:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這不是躲著嗎？！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.93,0:12:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別開玩笑了 你這傢伙！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:06.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35}13:10\N馬克在和2nd戰鬥\N匕首從右邊向著頭部刺來\N要小心啊！！\N13:20\N馬克抓住了2nd\N這樣一來就只剩下1st了\N真不愧是馬克\N13:30\N馬克找到了1st的藏身之所
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.63,0:12:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克 匕首會從右邊向著頭部刺來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.09,0:12:07.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.76,0:12:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃 會有飛踢從右邊過來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.15,0:12:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白癡嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.99,0:12:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是我這邊更快
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.77,0:12:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷口…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.10,0:12:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.69,0:12:29.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學我們是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.75,0:12:40.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35}7/7 13:00\N阿雪比起爸爸選擇了我哦！！\N今天可能是我人生中最棒的一天。\N7/7 13:10\N阿雪從廣播室那邊支援我。\N得好好表現呀！\N7/7 13:20\N阿雪在廣播室哦。要在那裡藏好哦。\N7/7 13:30\N阿雪被7th抓住了！！\N怎麼辦 我得去救他！\N7/7 13:40\N阿雪在和7th作戰的時候，受傷了。\N要趕快處理好傷口。
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.44,0:12:39.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1st在廣播室嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:42.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傢伙！我去把他抓來！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.29,0:12:43.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.79,0:12:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 真是沒長進啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.63,0:12:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,2對1怎麼可能贏呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.49,0:12:53.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 2對1不可能贏
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.36,0:12:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃被抓到了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.07,0:13:02.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1st
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.56,0:13:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不在？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.31,0:13:12.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼 日記上明明顯示的是這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:16.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說…這手機是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.19,0:13:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然2對1贏不了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.83,0:13:26.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,1st
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.14,0:13:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們準備的假貨
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:38.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35}13:20\N愛的記憶被1st的飛鏢射中死亡
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.85,0:13:37.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛…飛鏢！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.52,0:13:40.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正如由乃所料
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.27,0:13:44.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛 躲開飛鏢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.85,0:13:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被躲開了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.35,0:13:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.87,0:13:56.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果今天是最糟糕的一天
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.53,0:14:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就意味著明天只會比今天更好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.39,0:14:01.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.72,0:14:05.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克把我的最糟變成了最好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.49,0:14:09.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以希望能在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.13,0:14:15.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.94,0:14:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愛！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:19.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天花板…！？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:23.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了 有了這個降落傘
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.98,0:14:25.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們倆就能逃出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又能被阿雪誇獎了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.55,0:14:31.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.43,0:14:34.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把日記奪來就夠了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.89,0:14:37.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是這傢伙想要把阿雪殺掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.02,0:14:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做法總是太極端…了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.95,0:14:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.23,0:14:46.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.22,0:14:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下就能從這裡逃走了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.71,0:14:50.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.72,0:14:53.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:07.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.42,0:15:10.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.79,0:15:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該怎麼辦？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.07,0:15:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果也沒能把手機毀掉
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.26,0:15:27.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去欠款就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.76,0:15:29.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼 九郎！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.28,0:15:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,禮亞 為什麼會來這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.37,0:15:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小雪怎麼樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.58,0:15:38.63,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟發生什麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.04,0:15:39.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被麻煩的傢伙給纏住了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.65,0:15:40.70,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼你會在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.83,0:15:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是不想辦法逃掉的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.79,0:15:42.74,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我說清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.74,0:15:43.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.83,0:15:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你要帶我去哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:49.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然是警察那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.68,0:15:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不知道小雪怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.66,0:15:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們剛剛在一起吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.27,0:15:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我從警官那裡聽說了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.64,0:15:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之過來
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.21,0:15:59.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬆手
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.44,0:16:00.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 過來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.91,0:16:01.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.58,0:16:04.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是說了…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.55,0:16:05.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放手嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.10,0:16:13.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行啊 完全推不開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.10,0:16:16.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.40,0:16:19.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真可惜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.52,0:16:22.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35}13:10\N馬克在和2nd戰鬥\N匕首從右邊向著頭部刺來\N要小心啊！！\N13:20\N馬克抓住了2nd\N這樣一來就只剩下1st了\N真不愧是馬克\N13:30\N馬克找到了1st的藏身之所\N13:40\N馬克躲過塌方了\N13:50\N馬克好像受傷了\N得趕快進行處理
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.29,0:16:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克躲過塌方了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.03,0:16:24.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7th
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.75,0:16:27.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡的情況已經透過日記…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.97,0:16:30.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傳達給外面的馬克了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.76,0:16:33.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包括我馬上就會死這件事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.67,0:16:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有你們只能在這裡和塔一起完蛋的事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.89,0:16:42.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克馬上就能從這裡逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣一來…馬克就贏定了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.15,0:16:47.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.46,0:16:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.33,0:16:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這裡折磨你 引外面那男的進來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.03,0:16:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓他把這裡打開
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.14,0:16:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 由乃！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.72,0:16:59.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別妨礙我 阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在只有這個辦法了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.65,0:17:04.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算做這種事情也不會有用…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:06.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼聲音
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:10.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等著我 愛
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.78,0:17:12.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在就救你出來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.22,0:17:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.23,0:17:18.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是要成為神 兩個人永遠在一起嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.61,0:17:20.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論發生什麼我都要保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.20,0:17:21.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手 馬克
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.17,0:17:24.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正我…是會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.29,0:17:25.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 你別理他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.82,0:17:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣繼續挖
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:29.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這女人是人質
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.33,0:17:30.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別這樣 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.41,0:17:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還在說這種話啊 1st
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.95,0:17:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不弄髒自己的手 盡被2nd保護著
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.17,0:17:41.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不讓2nd做非人道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.74,0:17:44.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說的話根本就是胡扯
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.96,0:17:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是撬不起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.13,0:17:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼 從那邊一起抬啊 1st
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.21,0:17:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 7th
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.20,0:17:59.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不就正中由乃的心意了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.42,0:18:02.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直保護你到現在的人是誰啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.55,0:18:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有殺掉敵人的是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.64,0:18:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你只是把髒活都扔給了2nd而已啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.41,0:18:13.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是不行…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.91,0:18:16.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 2nd 你也來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.39,0:18:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發號施令的是我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.28,0:18:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你也一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.39,0:18:22.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊說著要幫1st
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.93,0:18:25.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊卻又在違背他的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.35,0:18:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種才不能算是「協助」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:31.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種叫做「自私」
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.81,0:18:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你給我適可而…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.95,0:18:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該適可而止的是你 你這小鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.37,0:18:40.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你覺得我是受到威脅才來的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.06,0:18:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看我 我從一開始就沒準備逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.84,0:18:49.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬…克 住手…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.96,0:18:53.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經夠了 我不久就會…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.98,0:18:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久就會死？關我屁事！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.70,0:19:00.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西都給我見鬼去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.84,0:19:07.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別把我們的「愛」和你們的「愛」相提並論
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.77,0:19:12.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,馬克…你
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.04,0:19:18.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉 失策了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.14,0:19:21.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃 快來幫忙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.87,0:19:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,三個人一起抬起來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.22,0:19:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但…但是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.41,0:19:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.56,0:19:29.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由乃你是真的喜歡我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.84,0:19:31.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是說只是個瘋子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.68,0:19:34.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.47,0:19:36.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我無法確信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.17,0:19:40.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我相信你吧 由乃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.67,0:20:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又一次 沒趕上
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:13.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35}14:10\N7th 美神愛因出血過多死亡\NDead End
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.80,0:20:12.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,勝利的是你們
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.55,0:20:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個帶走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.22,0:20:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7th…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.90,0:20:20.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別用那種同情敵人的眼神看我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:21.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.42,0:20:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「要成為神 兩個人永遠在一起」的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.51,0:20:41.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來是失敗了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35}14:10\N7th 美神愛因出血過多死亡\NDead End
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.78,0:20:41.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\fad(0,494)}14:10\N7th 美神愛因出血過多死亡\NDead End
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.90,0:20:43.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7\fs35\fad(424,0)}14:10\N7th 美神愛因出血過多死亡\N馬克來救我了\N果然馬克是最棒的\NDead End
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.17,0:20:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.48,0:20:47.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這也是…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.60,0:20:51.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一種「永遠」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.00,0:21:06.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要和爸爸媽媽都好好談談
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.87,0:21:08.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿雪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.67,0:21:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然由乃你可能討厭爸爸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他也確實有很多問題
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.23,0:21:19.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我還是希望爸爸和母親能夠和好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:22.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望由乃你能幫助我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.28,0:21:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪輝君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.82,0:21:36.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西島先生
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.64,0:21:37.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 雪輝君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.17,0:21:40.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冷靜下來 好好聽我說
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.64,0:21:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才在這裡…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.90,0:21:45.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,西島先生好像在說些什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.13,0:21:48.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 這些都沒有傳到我的耳中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.06,0:21:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為 那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.75,0:21:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事情怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.22,0:21:56.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35}7/7\N媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.37,0:21:54.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪輝君
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.52,0:21:55.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的媽媽…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.02,0:21:57.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\fs35}14:34\N死了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.57,0:22:08.57,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.59,0:22:42.84,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あとどれくらい失えば
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.59,0:22:42.84,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}到底還要失去多少東西
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.29,0:22:47.97,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}高鳴る鼓動を許される
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.29,0:22:47.97,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}這份高鳴的心跳才能被允許
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.17,0:22:53.55,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}赤くて涙
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.17,0:22:53.55,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}鮮紅的淚水
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.83,0:22:59.12,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}溢れるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.83,0:22:59.12,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}不斷的湧出
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:04.82,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}すべては未来を繋ぐ鍵
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.36,0:23:04.82,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一切都是連接未來的鑰匙
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.01,0:23:12.33,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}崩れる体に絆感じて
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.01,0:23:12.33,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}用崩潰的身體感受著羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.52,0:23:14.78,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}もう一度
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.52,0:23:14.78,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}再一次
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:24.75,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}君を守ると誓う
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:24.75,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}發誓要保護你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.85,0:23:27.44,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}(また守るために生きる)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.85,0:23:27.44,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}(為了再次守護而活下去)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:30.64,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}(僕ら僕であるために)
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.63,0:23:30.64,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}(為了我們能永遠在一起)
